m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this +5 unholy starknife confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, it has a chance to cast either slay living, confusion or crushing despair {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} on the target.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Four blades of this starknife bear four words in Aklo, the ancient language spoken by eldritch abominations: "DEFILEMENT", "DELIRIUM", "DESPAIR", "DEATH".

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this +5 holy starknife lands a hit, it dazzles the target for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d4{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}, and has a chance to cast blindness {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude save{/g}, {g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 21) on it.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: The holy weapon of Desna  goddess of luck, dreams and travels.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this +4 feybane starknife lands a hit, it has a chance to entangle the target.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon's wooden handle is alive, constantly growing little sprouts with tiny leaves.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +1 cold iron starknife deals an additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d3{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} to evil creatures.

Whenever the wielder of this +3 holy starknife confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g} with it, all their allies in a 40-foot area are affected with the effect of the prayer {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} for 6 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.

Whenever this +3 agile starknife lands a hit, the target must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Will saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 24) or become cursed. This curse reverses the effect of positive energy: if it {g|Encyclopedia:Healing}healed{/g} this creature before, now it deals {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}, and vice versa.

Whenever the wielder of this +4 shocking burst starknife lands a sneak {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack{/g} on an enemy, the enemy loses 5 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell_Resistance}spell resistance{/g} for 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}round{/g}.
This +5 caustic starknife deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}4d6{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}acid damage{/g} on sneak {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attacks{/g}.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
